### ================== RUTAS SIN AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los medicamentos (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/public

### Obtener medicamento por ID (SIN token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/public/1

### Crear un nuevo medicamento (SIN token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Paracetamol",
  "description": "Analgesico y antipirético",
  "stock": 100,
  "price": 5000,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar un medicamento (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/public/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Paracetamol 500mg",
  "description": "Analgesico y antipirético actualizado",
  "stock": 150,
  "price": 5500,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar un medicamento físicamente (SIN token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/public/1

### Desactivar un medicamento (SIN token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/public/1/deactivate

### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los medicamentos (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener medicamento por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo medicamento (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ibuprofeno",
  "description": "Anti-inflamatorio",
  "stock": 200,
  "price": 8000,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar un medicamento (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ibuprofeno 400mg",
  "description": "Anti-inflamatorio actualizado",
  "stock": 250,
  "price": 8500,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar un medicamento físicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Desactivar un medicamento (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/medicines/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
